# CareerMentor.AI - MERN + AI Project Guide

## 🚀 Project Summary

**CareerMentor.AI** is a comprehensive MERN stack platform enhanced with AI capabilities. It serves as a job tracker, interview preparation tool, community forum, resume analyzer, and mock interview platform. Ideal for students and job seekers.

---

## 🧱 Core Technologies

* **Frontend**: React.js, Tailwind CSS, React Router
* **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
* **Database**: MongoDB (Cloud via MongoDB Atlas)
* **Authentication**: JWT
* **AI Tools**:

  * OpenAI GPT-4 (for Resume Feedback, AI Q\&A, Mock Interviews)
  * OpenAI Whisper or Web Speech API (for Voice Input)
  * LangChain (optional, for advanced AI workflows)

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
project-root/
├── client/              # React frontend
├── server/              # Node/Express backend
├── models/              # Mongoose models
├── routes/              # API routes
├── controllers/         # Logic for each route
├── utils/ai/            # AI utility functions
├── middleware/          # Auth and error middleware
└── config/              # DB and API config
```

---

## 🗺️ Feature Modules

### 1. **Authentication (Login/Register)**

* JWT-based login system
* Role-based (Admin, User)

### 2. **Dashboard**

* Overview of job applications, interview tasks, AI feedback

### 3. **Job Tracker (from Project 6)**

* CRUD for job applications
* Status: Applied, Interviewed, Rejected, Hired

### 4. **Interview Prep (from Project 2)**

* CRUD for company-specific Q\&A
* Timer, checklist for revision

### 5. **Resume Analyzer (from Project 1)**

* Upload PDF Resume
* Use OpenAI to:

  * Analyze structure, skills, formatting
  * Return suggestions and rating

### 6. **College Connect Forum (from Project 3)**

* Post doubts, like, comment
* AI replies via OpenAI (thread starter or suggestions)

### 7. **AI Mock Interviews (from Project 10)**

* Select topic (DSA, React, etc.)
* AI asks questions, evaluates user input
* Scores or gives tips

---

## 📌 Step-by-Step Development Plan

### ✅ Week 1: Initial Setup & Auth

* [ ] Setup GitHub repo
* [ ] Create MERN boilerplate (React + Express)
* [ ] Setup MongoDB Atlas
* [ ] Implement Register/Login (JWT)

### ✅ Week 2: Resume Analyzer & Job Tracker

* [ ] Use `Multer` to upload PDF
* [ ] Use `pdf-parse` to extract text
* [ ] Integrate OpenAI GPT API for feedback
* [ ] Build Job Tracker frontend & backend (CRUD)

### ✅ Week 3: Interview Prep & Forum

* [ ] Interview Prep Page (Add, edit questions)
* [ ] Forum Page: Post doubts
* [ ] Add AI suggestion logic using GPT-4

### ✅ Week 4: AI Interview + Voice

* [ ] Create Mock Interview bot with OpenAI
* [ ] Add Web Speech API for voice input
* [ ] Save answers, generate feedback

### ✅ Week 5: Finishing & Deploying

* [ ] UI Polishing with Tailwind CSS
* [ ] Error Handling, Loading States
* [ ] Deploy Frontend (Netlify) + Backend (Render)
* [ ] Set up MongoDB Atlas connection string

---

## 🔌 Required APIs and Tools

### 🔑 OpenAI API

* **Signup**: [https://platform.openai.com/signup](https://platform.openai.com/signup)
* **Docs**: [https://platform.openai.com/docs](https://platform.openai.com/docs)
* **Models Used**: `gpt-4`, `gpt-3.5-turbo`, `whisper-1`
* **Pricing**: [https://openai.com/pricing](https://openai.com/pricing)

### 📁 PDF Parsing

* Library: `pdf-parse`
* GitHub: [https://github.com/modesty/pdf-parse](https://github.com/modesty/pdf-parse)

### 📢 Web Speech API (Browser-based voice input)

* Docs: [https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web\_Speech\_API](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Speech_API)

### 🧠 LangChain (Optional for advanced chains)

* Docs: [https://js.langchain.com](https://js.langchain.com)

### 🌐 MongoDB Atlas

* Setup: [https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas/register](https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas/register)
* Free tier available

### 🖼 Deployment

* **Frontend**: [https://www.netlify.com/](https://www.netlify.com/)
* **Backend**: [https://render.com/](https://render.com/)

